<div>
  <video 
    src="http://techslides.com/demos/sample-videos/small.mp4"
    ontimeupdate={{action "updateCurrentTime"}}
    onloadeddata={{action "onLoad"}}
    controls
  ></video>
</div>
<br>
<div>
  This gets rerendered at each update -> Current Time Full: {{this.currentTime}}
</div>
<br>
<div>
  This gets rerendered only when full seconds change -> Current Time Truncated: {{this.currentTimeTruncated}}
</div>
<br>
<div>
  This gets rerendered at each update, even though should only when full seconds change:
  <svg width="300px" height="10px">
    <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)" stroke="none"/>

    <rect
      width="{{this.progress}}%"
      height="100%"
      fill="rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85)"
      stroke="none"
    />
  </svg>
</div>